### Sambandh API examples — verification flow

@host = http://localhost:3010
@token = PASTE_TOKEN

### Submit profession for verification
### Documents must be base64-encoded
POST {{host}}/api/verification/profession
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Mechanical Engineer",
  "company": "Tata Motors",
  "startDate": "2020-07-01",
  "linkedinUrl": "https://linkedin.com/in/arjunkalita",
  "documents": [
    {
      "type": "offer_letter",
      "filename": "tata_offer.pdf",
      "base64": "JVBERi0xLjQKJ..."
    },
    {
      "type": "company_id",
      "filename": "id_card.jpg",
      "base64": "/9j/4AAQSkZJRg..."
    }
  ]
}

###

### Get my verifications
GET {{host}}/api/verification/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### --- Admin only ---

### Approve a verification
POST {{host}}/api/verification/admin/PASTE_VERIFICATION_ID/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Reject a verification
POST {{host}}/api/verification/admin/PASTE_VERIFICATION_ID/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Offer letter unclear, please re-upload a clearer scan."
}

###
